LocaleResource.Name: Admin.FoxNetSoft.Plugin.Misc.Pagespeed.CssStyleUrl.Hint
LocaleResource.Value:
If you need to minify one css style file you can do it.
Provide the css style Url.
Example:
'http://www.yoursite.com/style.min.css' or 'http://www.yoursite.com/style.css'.
Plugin will create a new minified css file with the new name.
Example:
1. You want to minify the file 'http://www.yoursite.com/style.css'
Plugin will create the new file 'http://www.yoursite.com/style.min.css'
2. You want to minify the file 'http://www.yoursite.com/style.min.css'
Plugin will update existing file 'http://www.yoursite.com/style.min.css'

LocaleResource.Name: Admin.FoxNetSoft.Plugin.Misc.Pagespeed.TaskCssStyle.Hint
LocaleResource.Value: Minify all css styles. Plugin will do it by scheduler. If you want to do it at once you can run the task manually.

LocaleResource.Name: Admin.FoxNetSoft.Plugin.Misc.Pagespeed.JavaScriptUrl.Hint
LocaleResource.Value:
If you need to minify one js file you can do it.
Provide the JavaScript Url.
Example:
'http://www.yoursite.com/jquery.min.js' or 'http://www.yoursite.com/jquery.js'.
Plugin will create a new minified js with the new name.
Example:
1. You want to minify the file 'http://www.yoursite.com/jquery.js'
Plugin will create the new file 'http://www.yoursite.com/jquery.min.js'
2. You want to minify the file 'http://www.yoursite.com/jquery.min.js'
Plugin will update existing file 'http://www.yoursite.com/jquery.min.js'

LocaleResource.Name: Admin.FoxNetSoft.Plugin.Misc.Pagespeed.TaskJavaScript.Hint
LocaleResource.Value: Minify all js file. Plugin will do it by scheduler. If you want to do it at once you can run the task manually.
